|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-1612">0xC001F083</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-1612">0xC001F083</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-1613">-1073614717</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-1613">-1073614717</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-1614">DTS_E_LOADCHECKPOINT</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-1614">DTS_E_LOADCHECKPOINT</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-1615">由于无法加载检查点文件，包在执行期间失败。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-1615">The package failed during execution because the checkpoint file cannot be loaded.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-1616">要继续执行包，需要检查点文件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-1616">Further execution of the package requires a checkpoint file.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-1617">如果 CheckpointUsage 属性设置为 ALWAYS (指定包始终重新启动)，通常会出现此错误。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-1617">This error usually occurs when the CheckpointUsage property is set to ALWAYS, which specifies that the package always restarts.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-1618">0xC001F185</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-1618">0xC001F185</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-1619">-1073614459</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-1619">-1073614459</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-1620">DTS_E_NOEVALEXPRESSION</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-1620">DTS_E_NOEVALEXPRESSION</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-1621">For 循环“%1”的求值条件表达式为空。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-1621">The evaluation condition expression on the For Loop "%1" is empty.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-1622">For 循环中必须有布尔求值表达式。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-1622">There must be a Boolean evaluation expression in the For Loop.</span></span>|

|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4094">0xC004701F</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4094">0xC004701F</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4095">-1073450977</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4095">-1073450977</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4096">DTS_E_CANTCOMPARE</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4096">DTS_E_CANTCOMPARE</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4097">数据类型“%1”不可比较。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4097">The data type "%1" cannot be compared.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4098">不支持与该数据类型比较，因此不能对其进行排序或将其用作键。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4098">Comparison of that data type is not supported, so it cannot be sorted or used as a key.</span></span>|

|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4103">0xC0047021</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4103">0xC0047021</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4104">-1073450975</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4104">-1073450975</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4105">DTS_E_THREADFAILED</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4105">DTS_E_THREADFAILED</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4106">SSIS 错误代码 DTS_E_THREADFAILED。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4106">SSIS Error Code DTS_E_THREADFAILED.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4107">线程“%1”已退出，错误代码为 0x%2!8.8X!。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4107">Thread "%1" has exited with error code 0x%2!8.8X!.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4108">可能在此之前已经发出错误消息，提供了有关线程退出原因的详细信息。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4108">There may be error messages posted before this with more information on why the thread has exited.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4109">0xC0047022</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4109">0xC0047022</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4110">-1073450974</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4110">-1073450974</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4111">DTS_E_PROCESSINPUTFAILED</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4111">DTS_E_PROCESSINPUTFAILED</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4112">SSIS 错误代码 DTS_E_PROCESSINPUTFAILED。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4112">SSIS Error Code DTS_E_PROCESSINPUTFAILED.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4113">处理输入“%4”(%5!d!) 时，组件“%1”(%2!d!)的 ProcessInput 方法失败，错误代码为 0x%3!8.8X!</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4113">The ProcessInput method on component "%1" (%2!d!) failed with error code 0x%3!8.8X!</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4114">。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4114">while processing input "%4" (%5!d!).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4115">标识的这个组件从 ProcessInput 方法返回了一个错误。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4115">The identified component returned an error from the ProcessInput method.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4116">虽然该错误是此组件特有的，但却是致命的，将导致数据流任务停止运行。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4116">The error is specific to the component, but the error is fatal and will cause the Data Flow task to stop running.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4117">可能在此之前已经发出错误消息，提供了有关失败的详细信息。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4117">There may be error messages posted before this with more information about the failure.</span></span>|

|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4142">0xC004702B</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4142">0xC004702B</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4143">-1073450965</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4143">-1073450965</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4144">DTS_E_INCORRECTCOMPONENTVIEWID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4144">DTS_E_INCORRECTCOMPONENTVIEWID</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4145">组件视图 ID 不正确。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4145">The component view ID is incorrect.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4146">此组件视图可能不同步。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4146">The component view may be out of synchronization.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4147">请尝试释放此组件视图，然后重新创建它。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4147">Try releasing the component view and recreating it.</span></span>|

|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4164">0xC004702F</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4164">0xC004702F</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4165">-1073450961</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4165">-1073450961</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4166">DTS_E_INVALIDUSESDISPOSITIONSVALUE</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4166">DTS_E_INVALIDUSESDISPOSITIONSVALUE</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4167">不能更改 UsesDispositions 属性的初始值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4167">The UsesDispositions property cannot be changed from its initial value.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4168">如果编辑了 XML 并修改了 UsesDispositions 值，就会发生这种情况。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4168">This occurs when the XML is edited and the UsesDispositions value is modified.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4169">该值是在将组件添加到包时由该组件设置的，不可以更改。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4169">This value is set by the component when it is added to the package and is not allowed to change.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4170">0xC0047030</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4170">0xC0047030</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4171">-1073450960</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4171">-1073450960</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4172">DTS_E_THREADFAILEDINITIALIZE</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4172">DTS_E_THREADFAILEDINITIALIZE</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4173">数据流任务无法初始化一个必需的线程，因此无法开始执行。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4173">The Data Flow task failed to initialize a required thread and cannot begin execution.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4174">该线程先前已报告了一个特定的错误。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4174">The thread previously reported a specific error.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4175">0xC0047031</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4175">0xC0047031</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4176">-1073450959</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4176">-1073450959</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4177">DTS_E_THREADFAILEDCREATE</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4177">DTS_E_THREADFAILEDCREATE</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4178">数据流任务无法创建一个必需的线程，因此无法开始运行。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4178">The Data Flow task failed to create a required thread and cannot begin running.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4179">内存不足时通常会发生这种情况。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4179">The usually occurs when there is an out-of-memory state.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4180">0xC0047032</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4180">0xC0047032</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4181">-1073450958</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4181">-1073450958</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4182">DTS_E_EXECUTIONTREECYCLEADDINGSYNCHRONOUSINPUT</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4182">DTS_E_EXECUTIONTREECYCLEADDINGSYNCHRONOUSINPUT</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4183">不能将“%1”的同步输入设置为“%2”，因为这会产生循环。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4183">The synchronous input of "%1" cannot be set to "%2" because a cycle would be created.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4184">0xC0047033</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4184">0xC0047033</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4185">-1073450957</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4185">-1073450957</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4186">DTS_E_INVALIDCUSTOMPROPERTYNAME</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4186">DTS_E_INVALIDCUSTOMPROPERTYNAME</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4187">名为“%1”的自定义属性无效，因为已有一个同名的常用属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4187">A custom property named "%1" is invalid because there is a stock property with that name.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4188">自定义属性不能与同一对象的常用属性同名。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4188">A custom property cannot have the same name as a stock property on the same object.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4189">0xC0047035</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4189">0xC0047035</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4190">-1073450955</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4190">-1073450955</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4191">DTS_E_BUFFERLOCKUNDERFLOW</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4191">DTS_E_BUFFERLOCKUNDERFLOW</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4192">缓冲区已解锁。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4192">The buffer was already unlocked.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4193">0xC0047036</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4193">0xC0047036</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4194">-1073450954</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4194">-1073450954</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4195">DTS_E_INDIVIDUALCACHEINTERFACESFAILED</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4195">DTS_E_INDIVIDUALCACHEINTERFACESFAILED</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4196">%1 初始化失败，返回的错误代码为 0x%2!8.8X!。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4196">%1 failed initialization and returned error code 0x%2!8.8X!.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4197">0xC0047037</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4197">0xC0047037</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4198">-1073450953</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4198">-1073450953</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4199">DTS_E_INDIVIDUALRELEASEINTERFACESFAILED</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4199">DTS_E_INDIVIDUALRELEASEINTERFACESFAILED</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4200">%1 在关闭过程中失败，返回的错误代码为 0x%2!8.8X!。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4200">%1 failed during shut down and returned error code 0x%2!8.8X!.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4201">某个组件无法释放其接口。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4201">A component failed to release its interfaces.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4202">0xC0047038</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4202">0xC0047038</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4203">-1073450952</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4203">-1073450952</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4204">DTS_E_PRIMEOUTPUTFAILED</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4204">DTS_E_PRIMEOUTPUTFAILED</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4205">SSIS 错误代码 DTS_E_PRIMEOUTPUTFAILED。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4205">SSIS Error Code DTS_E_PRIMEOUTPUTFAILED.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4206">%1 的 PrimeOutput 方法返回了错误代码 0x%2!8.8X!。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4206">The PrimeOutput method on %1 returned error code 0x%2!8.8X!.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4207">管道引擎调用 PrimeOutput() 时该组件返回了一个失败代码。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4207">The component returned a failure code when the pipeline engine called PrimeOutput().</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4208">虽然该失败代码只与该组件有关，但这个错误是致命的，管道已停止执行。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4208">The meaning of the failure code is defined by the component, but the error is fatal and the pipeline stopped executing.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4209">可能在此之前已经发出错误消息，提供了有关失败的详细信息。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4209">There may be error messages posted before this with more information about the failure.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4210">0xC0047039</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4210">0xC0047039</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4211">-1073450951</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4211">-1073450951</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4212">DTS_E_THREADCANCELLED</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4212">DTS_E_THREADCANCELLED</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4213">SSIS 错误代码 DTS_E_THREADCANCELLED。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4213">SSIS Error Code DTS_E_THREADCANCELLED.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4214">线程“%1”接收到关闭信号，正在终止。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4214">Thread "%1" received a shutdown signal and is terminating.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4215">原因是用户请求了关闭，或另一线程中的错误导致该管道关闭。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4215">The user requested a shutdown, or an error in another thread is causing the pipeline to shutdown.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4216">可能在此之前已经发出错误消息，提供了有关取消线程的原因的详细信息。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4216">There may be error messages posted before this with more information on why the thread was cancelled.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4217">0xC004703A</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4217">0xC004703A</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4218">-1073450950</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4218">-1073450950</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4219">DTS_E_DISTRIBUTORCANTSETPROPERTY</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4219">DTS_E_DISTRIBUTORCANTSETPROPERTY</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4220">由于出现错误 0x%8.8X，线程“%1”的分发服务器无法初始化组件“%3”的属性“%2”。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4220">Distributor for thread "%1" failed to initialize property "%2" on component "%3" because of error 0x%8.8X.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4221">该分发服务器无法初始化该组件的属性且无法继续运行。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4221">The distributor could not initialize the component's property and cannot continue running.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4222">0xC004703B</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4222">0xC004703B</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4223">-1073450949</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4223">-1073450949</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4224">DTS_E_CANTREGISTERVIEWBUFFERTYPE</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4224">DTS_E_CANTREGISTERVIEWBUFFERTYPE</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4225">数据流任务无法注册某个视图缓冲区类型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4225">The Data Flow task cannot register a view buffer type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4226">该类型有 %1!d!</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4226">The type had %1!d!</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4227">列，用于输入 ID %2!d!。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4227">columns and was for input ID %2!d!.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4228">0xC004703F</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4228">0xC004703F</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4229">-1073450945</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4229">-1073450945</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4230">DTS_E_CANTCREATEEXECUTIONTREE</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4230">DTS_E_CANTCREATEEXECUTIONTREE</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4231">内存不足，无法创建执行树。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4231">There is not enough memory to create an execution tree.</span></span>|

|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4240">0xC0047043</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4240">0xC0047043</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4241">-1073450941</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4241">-1073450941</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4242">DTS_E_CANTCREATECOMPONENTVIEW</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4242">DTS_E_CANTCREATECOMPONENTVIEW</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4243">无法创建组件视图，因为已经有一个组件视图。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4243">Cannot create a component view because another one already exists.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4244">不能同时存在多个组件视图。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4244">Only one component view can exist at a time.</span></span>|

|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4359">0xC0047063</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4359">0xC0047063</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4360">-1073450909</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4360">-1073450909</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4361">DTS_E_SCHEDULERMEMORY</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4361">DTS_E_SCHEDULERMEMORY</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4362">数据流引擎计划程序无法为执行结构分配足够的内存。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4362">The Data Flow engine scheduler cannot allocate enough memory for the execution structures.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4363">在开始执行之前系统内存不足。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4363">The system was low on memory before execution started.</span></span>|

|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4381">0xC0047068</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4381">0xC0047068</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4382">-1073450904</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4382">-1073450904</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4383">DTS_E_SORTEDOUTPUTHASINVALIDSORTKEYPOSITION</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4383">DTS_E_SORTEDOUTPUTHASINVALIDSORTKEYPOSITION</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4384">“%1”有一个非零 SortKeyPosition，但是其值(%2!ld!)太大。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4384">"%1" has a non-zero SortKeyPosition, but its value (%2!ld!) is too large.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4385">该值必须小于等于列数。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4385">It must be less than or equal to the number of columns.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4386">0xC004706A</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4386">0xC004706A</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4387">-1073450902</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4387">-1073450902</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4388">DTS_E_SORTEDOUTPUTHASINVALIDSORTKEYPOSITIONS</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4388">DTS_E_SORTEDOUTPUTHASINVALIDSORTKEYPOSITIONS</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4389">%1 的 IsSorted 属性设置为 TRUE，但是非零输出列 SortKeyPositions 的绝对值没有形成一个以 1 开头的单调递增序列。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4389">The IsSorted property of %1 is set to TRUE, but the absolute values of the non-zero output column SortKeyPositions do not form a monotonically increasing sequence, starting at one.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4390">0xC004706B</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4390">0xC004706B</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4391">-1073450901</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4391">-1073450901</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4392">DTS_E_INDIVIDUALVALIDATIONSTATUSFAILED</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4392">DTS_E_INDIVIDUALVALIDATIONSTATUSFAILED</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4393">“%1”验证失败，返回的验证状态为“%2”。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4393">"%1" failed validation and returned validation status "%2".</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4394">0xC004706C</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4394">0xC004706C</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4395">-1073450900</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4395">-1073450900</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4396">DTS_E_CANTCREATECOMPONENT</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4396">DTS_E_CANTCREATECOMPONENT</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4397">无法创建组件“%1!s!”，</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4397">Component "%1!s!"</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4398">返回了错误代码 0x%2!8.8X!</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4398">could not be created and returned error code 0x%2!8.8X!</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4399">“%3!s!”。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4399">"%3!s!".</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4400">请确保该组件已正确注册。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4400">Make sure that the component is registered correctly.</span></span>|

|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4405">0xC004706E</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4405">0xC004706E</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4406">-1073450898</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4406">-1073450898</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4407">DTS_E_COMPONENTNOTFOUND</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4407">DTS_E_COMPONENTNOTFOUND</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4408">即使包含“%1”的模块已经注册，也找不到该模块。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4408">The module containing "%1" cannot be located, even though it is registered.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4409">0xC004706F</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4409">0xC004706F</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4410">-1073450897</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4410">-1073450897</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4411">DTS_E_BINARYCODENOTFOUND</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4411">DTS_E_BINARYCODENOTFOUND</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4412">根据配置，脚本组件应预编译该脚本，但找不到二进制代码。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4412">The script component is configured to pre-compile the script, but binary code is not found.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4413">请单击“设计脚本”按钮，使用脚本组件编辑器中的 IDE 来生成二进制代码。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4413">Please visit the IDE in Script Component Editor by clicking Design Script button to cause binary code to be generated.</span></span>|

|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4419">0xC0047071</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4419">0xC0047071</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4420">-1073450895</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4420">-1073450895</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4421">DTS_E_SYNCHRONOUSIDMISMATCH</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4421">DTS_E_SYNCHRONOUSIDMISMATCH</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4422">“%1”的 SynchronousInputID 属性为 %2!d!，但应为 %3!d!</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4422">The SynchronousInputID property on "%1" was %2!d!, and %3!d!</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4423">。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4423">was expected.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4424">0xC0047072</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4424">0xC0047072</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4425">-1073450894</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4425">-1073450894</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4426">DTS_E_OBJECTIDNOTFOUND</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4426">DTS_E_OBJECTIDNOTFOUND</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4427">不存在 ID 为 %1!d! 的对象。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4427">No object exists with the ID %1!d!.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4428">0xC0047073</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4428">0xC0047073</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4429">-1073450893</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4429">-1073450893</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4430">DTS_E_OBJECTIDLOOKUPFAILED</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4430">DTS_E_OBJECTIDLOOKUPFAILED</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4431">找不到 ID 为 %1!d! 的对象，</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4431">Unable to locate an object with ID %1!d!</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4432">因为错误代码为 0x%2!8.8X!。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4432">because of the error code 0x%2!8.8X!.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4433">0xC0047074</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4433">0xC0047074</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4434">-1073450892</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4434">-1073450892</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4435">DTS_E_INVALIDCODEPAGE</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4435">DTS_E_INVALIDCODEPAGE</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4436">对输出列“%2”(%3!d!)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4436">The code page %1!d!</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4437">指定的代码页 %1!d! 无效。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4437">specified on output column "%2" (%3!d!) is not valid.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4438">请为输出列“%2”另选一个代码页。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4438">Select a different code page for output column "%2".</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4439">0xC0047075</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4439">0xC0047075</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4440">-1073450891</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4440">-1073450891</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4441">DTS_E_INDIVIDUALPUTEVENTINFOSFAILED</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4441">DTS_E_INDIVIDUALPUTEVENTINFOSFAILED</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4442">“%1”无法缓存 EventInfos 集合，返回的错误代码为 0x%2!8.8X!。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4442">The EventInfos collection could not be cached by "%1" and returned error code 0x%2!8.8X!.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4443">0xC0047077</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4443">0xC0047077</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4444">-1073450889</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4444">-1073450889</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4445">DTS_E_DUPLICATEOUTPUTCOLUMNNAMES</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4445">DTS_E_DUPLICATEOUTPUTCOLUMNNAMES</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4446">“%1”的名称是一个重复名称。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4446">The name for "%1" is a duplicate.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4447">所有名称都必须是唯一的。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4447">All names must be unique.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4448">0xC0047078</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4448">0xC0047078</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4449">-1073450888</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4449">-1073450888</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4450">DTS_E_NOOUTPUTCOLUMNFORINPUTCOLUMN</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4450">DTS_E_NOOUTPUTCOLUMNFORINPUTCOLUMN</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4451">没有与输入列“%1”(%2!d!)关联的输出列。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4451">There is no output column associated with input column "%1" (%2!d!).</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4452">0xC0047079</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4452">0xC0047079</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4453">-1073450887</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4453">-1073450887</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4454">DTS_E_EXCLGRPNOSYNCINP</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4454">DTS_E_EXCLGRPNOSYNCINP</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4455">“%1”有一个从根源扩展而来的虚拟缓冲区。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4455">"%1" has a virtual buffer extending from a root source.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4456">某个非零排除组的同步输入为零。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4456">There is an exclusion group that is not zero with a synchronous input that is zero.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4457">0xC004707A</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4457">0xC004707A</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4458">-1073450886</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4458">-1073450886</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4459">DTS_E_ERROROUTCANTBEONSYNCNONEXCLUSIVEOUTPUT</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4459">DTS_E_ERROROUTCANTBEONSYNCNONEXCLUSIVEOUTPUT</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4460">“%1”不能是错误输出，因为不能将错误输出放在同步的非排他输出中。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4460">"%1" cannot be an error output because error outputs cannot be placed on synchronous, non-exclusive outputs.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4461">0xC004707B</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4461">0xC004707B</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4462">-1073450885</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4462">-1073450885</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4463">DTS_E_EXPREVALDIVBYZERO</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4463">DTS_E_EXPREVALDIVBYZERO</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4464">出现被零除错误。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4464">A divide-by-zero error occurred.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4465">表达式“%1”的右侧操作数的值为零。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4465">The right side operand evaluates to zero in the expression "%1".</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4466">0xC004707C</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4466">0xC004707C</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4467">-1073450884</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4467">-1073450884</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4468">DTS_E_EXPREVALLITERALOVERFLOW</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4468">DTS_E_EXPREVALLITERALOVERFLOW</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4469">文本“%1”太大，在 %2 类型中容纳不下。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4469">The literal "%1" is too large to fit into type %2.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4470">此文本的大小溢出了该类型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4470">The magnitude of the literal overflows the type.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4471">0xC004707D</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4471">0xC004707D</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4472">-1073450883</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4472">-1073450883</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4473">DTS_E_EXPREVALBINARYOPNUMERICOVERFLOW</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4473">DTS_E_EXPREVALBINARYOPNUMERICOVERFLOW</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4474">对数据类型 %2 和 %3 进行二元运算“%1”得到的结果超出了数值类型的最大大小。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4474">The result of the binary operation "%1" on data types %2 and %3 exceeds the maximum size for numeric types.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4475">若不降低精度或减少小数位数，就无法将操作数类型隐式转换为数值(DT_NUMERIC)结果。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4475">The operand types could not be implicitly cast into a numeric (DT_NUMERIC) result without loss of precision or scale.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4476">若要执行此运算，需要使用转换运算符来显式转换两个操作数或其中的一个操作数。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4476">To perform this operation, one or both operands need to be explicitly cast with a cast operator.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4477">0xC004707E</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4477">0xC004707E</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4478">-1073450882</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4478">-1073450882</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4479">DTS_E_EXPREVALBINARYOPOVERFLOW</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4479">DTS_E_EXPREVALBINARYOPOVERFLOW</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4480">二元运算“%1”的结果超出了结果数据类型“%2”的最大大小。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4480">The result of the binary operation "%1" exceeds the maximum size for result data type "%2".</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4481">运算结果的大小溢出了结果类型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4481">The magnitude of the result of the operation overflows the type of the result.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4482">0xC004707F</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4482">0xC004707F</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4483">-1073450881</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4483">-1073450881</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4484">DTS_E_EXPREVALFUNCTIONOVERFLOW</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4484">DTS_E_EXPREVALFUNCTIONOVERFLOW</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4485">函数调用“%1”的结果太大，“%2”类型中容纳不下。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4485">The result of the function call "%1" is too large to fit in type "%2".</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4486">函数调用结果的大小溢出了该操作数的类型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4486">The magnitude of the result of the function call overflows the type of the operand.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4487">可能需要显式转换为较大的类型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4487">An explicit cast to a larger type may be required.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4488">0xC0047080</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4488">0xC0047080</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4489">-1073450880</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4489">-1073450880</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4490">DTS_E_EXPREVALBINARYTYPEMISMATCH</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4490">DTS_E_EXPREVALBINARYTYPEMISMATCH</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4491">数据类型“%1”和“%2”与二元运算符“%3”不兼容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4491">The data types "%1" and "%2" are incompatible for binary operator "%3".</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4492">无法将操作数类型隐式转换为与此运算兼容的类型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4492">The operand types could not be implicitly cast into compatible types for the operation.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4493">若要执行此运算，需要使用转换运算符来显式转换两个操作数或其中的一个操作数。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4493">To perform this operation, one or both operands need to be explicitly cast with a cast operator.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4494">0xC0047081</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4494">0xC0047081</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4495">-1073450879</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4495">-1073450879</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4496">DTS_E_EXPREVALUNSUPPORTEDBINARYTYPE</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4496">DTS_E_EXPREVALUNSUPPORTEDBINARYTYPE</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4497">数据类型“%1”不能用于二元运算符“%2”。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4497">The data type "%1" cannot be used with binary operator "%2".</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4498">此运算不支持两个操作数的类型或其中一个操作数的类型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4498">The type of one or both of the operands is not supported for the operation.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4499">若要执行此运算，需要使用转换运算符来显式转换两个操作数或其中的一个操作数。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4499">To perform this operation, one or both operands need to be explicitly cast with a cast operator.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4500">0xC0047082</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4500">0xC0047082</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4501">-1073450878</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4501">-1073450878</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4502">DTS_E_EXPREVALBINARYSIGNMISMATCH</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4502">DTS_E_EXPREVALBINARYSIGNMISMATCH</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4503">在运算“%2”中，位二元运算符“%1”存在符号不匹配的情况。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4503">There is a sign mismatch for the bitwise binary operator "%1" in operation "%2".</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4504">此运算符的两个操作数必须同时为正或同时为负。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4504">Both operands for this operator must be positive or negative.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4505">0xC0047083</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4505">0xC0047083</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4506">-1073450877</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4506">-1073450877</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4507">DTS_E_EXPREVALBINARYOPERATIONFAILED</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4507">DTS_E_EXPREVALBINARYOPERATIONFAILED</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4508">二元运算“%1”失败，错误代码为 0x%2!8.8X!。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4508">The binary operation "%1" failed with error code 0x%2!8.8X!.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4509">可能出现了内部错误，或者内存不足。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4509">An internal error occurred, or an out-of-memory condition exists.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4510">0xC0047084</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4510">0xC0047084</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4511">-1073450876</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4511">-1073450876</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4512">DTS_E_EXPREVALBINARYOPERATIONSETTYPEFAILED</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4512">DTS_E_EXPREVALBINARYOPERATIONSETTYPEFAILED</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4513">尝试设置二元运算“%1”的结果类型失败，错误代码为 0x%2!8.8X!。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4513">Attempt to set the result type of binary operation "%1" failed with error code 0x%2!8.8X!.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4514">0xC0047085</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4514">0xC0047085</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4515">-1073450875</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4515">-1073450875</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4516">DTS_E_EXPREVALSTRINGCOMPARISONFAILED</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4516">DTS_E_EXPREVALSTRINGCOMPARISONFAILED</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4517">比较“%1”和字符串“%2”失败。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4517">Comparing "%1" to string "%2" failed.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4518">0xC0047086</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4518">0xC0047086</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4519">-1073450874</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4519">-1073450874</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4520">DTS_E_EXPREVALUNSUPPORTEDUNNARYTYPE</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4520">DTS_E_EXPREVALUNSUPPORTEDUNNARYTYPE</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4521">数据类型“%1”不能用于一元运算符“%2”。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4521">The data type "%1" cannot be used with unary operator "%2".</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4522">此运算不支持此操作数类型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4522">This operand type is not supported for the operation.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4523">若要执行此运算，需要使用转换运算符显式转换该操作数。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4523">To perform this operation, the operand needs to be explicitly cast with a cast operator.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4524">0xC0047087</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4524">0xC0047087</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4525">-1073450873</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4525">-1073450873</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4526">DTS_E_EXPREVALUNARYOPERATIONFAILED</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4526">DTS_E_EXPREVALUNARYOPERATIONFAILED</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4527">二元运算“%1”失败，错误代码为 0x%2!8.8X!。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4527">The unary operation "%1" failed with error code 0x%2!8.8X!.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4528">可能出现了内部错误，或者内存不足。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4528">An internal error occurred, or there is an out-of-memory condition.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4529">0xC0047088</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4529">0xC0047088</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4530">-1073450872</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4530">-1073450872</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4531">DTS_E_EXPREVALUNARYOPERATIONSETTYPEFAILED</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4531">DTS_E_EXPREVALUNARYOPERATIONSETTYPEFAILED</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4532">尝试设置一元运算“%1”的结果类型失败，错误代码为 0x%2!8.8X!。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4532">Attempt to set the result type of unary operation "%1" failed with error code 0x%2!8.8X!.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4533">0xC0047089</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4533">0xC0047089</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4534">-1073450871</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4534">-1073450871</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4535">DTS_E_EXPREVALPARAMTYPEMISMATCH</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4535">DTS_E_EXPREVALPARAMTYPEMISMATCH</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4536">对于参数 %3!d!，函数“%1”不支持数据类型“%2”。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4536">The function "%1" does not support the data type "%2" for parameter number %3!d!.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4537">无法将参数类型隐式转换为与该函数兼容的类型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4537">The type of the parameter could not be implicitly cast into a compatible type for the function.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4538">若要执行此运算，需要使用转换运算符显式转换该操作数。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4538">To perform this operation, the operand needs to be explicitly cast with a cast operator.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4539">0xC004708A</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4539">0xC004708A</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4540">-1073450870</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4540">-1073450870</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4541">DTS_E_EXPREVALINVALIDFUNCTION</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4541">DTS_E_EXPREVALINVALIDFUNCTION</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4542">无法识别函数“%1”。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4542">The function "%1" was not recognized.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4543">函数名称不正确或者不存在。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4543">Either the function name is incorrect or does not exist.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4544">0xC004708B</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4544">0xC004708B</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4545">-1073450869</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4545">-1073450869</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4546">DTS_E_EXPREVALFNSUBSTRINGINVALIDLENGTH</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4546">DTS_E_EXPREVALFNSUBSTRINGINVALIDLENGTH</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4547">长度 %1!d!</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4547">The length %1!d!</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4548">对函数“%2”无效。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4548">is not valid for function "%2".</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4549">长度参数不能为负值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4549">The length parameter cannot be negative.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4550">请将长度参数更改为零或正数。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4550">Change the length parameter to zero or a positive value.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4551">0xC004708C</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4551">0xC004708C</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4552">-1073450868</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4552">-1073450868</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4553">DTS_E_EXPREVALFNSUBSTRINGINVALIDSTARTINDEX</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4553">DTS_E_EXPREVALFNSUBSTRINGINVALIDSTARTINDEX</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4554">起始索引 %1!d!</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4554">The start index %1!d!</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4555">对函数“%2”无效。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4555">is not valid for function "%2".</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4556">起始索引值必须是大于 0 的整数。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4556">The start index value must be an integer greater than 0.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4557">起始索引是从 1 开始的，而不是从 0 开始的。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4557">Start index is one-based, not zero-based.</span></span>|

|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4566">0xC0047090</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4566">0xC0047090</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4567">-1073450864</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4567">-1073450864</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4568">DTS_E_EXPREVALINVALIDNULLPARAM</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4568">DTS_E_EXPREVALINVALIDNULLPARAM</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4569">函数 NULL 中数据类型为“%2”的参数 %1!d!</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4569">Parameter number %1!d!</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4570">无效。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4570">of the function NULL with data type "%2" is not valid.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4571">NULL() 的参数必须是静态的，不能包含输入列之类的动态元素。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4571">The parameters of NULL() must be static, and cannot contain dynamic elements such as input columns.</span></span>|

|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4633">0xC004709C</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4633">0xC004709C</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4634">-1073450852</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4634">-1073450852</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4635">DTS_E_EXPREVALBUILDSTRINGFAILED</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4635">DTS_E_EXPREVALBUILDSTRINGFAILED</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4636">尝试生成表达式的字符串表示形式失败，错误代码为 0x%1!8.8X!。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4636">Attempt to generate a string representation of the expression failed with error code 0x%1!8.8X!.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4637">未能生成表示表达式的可显示字符串。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4637">Failed when attempting to generate a displayable string that represents the expression.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4638">0xC004709D</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4638">0xC004709D</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4639">-1073450851</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4639">-1073450851</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4640">DTS_E_EXPREVALCANNOTCONVERTRESULT</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4640">DTS_E_EXPREVALCANNOTCONVERTRESULT</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4641">无法将表达式结果数据类型“%1”转换为列数据类型“%2”。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4641">Cannot convert the expression result data type "%1" to the column data type "%2".</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4642">应将表达式的结果写入输入/输出列，但无法将表达式的数据类型转换为列的数据类型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4642">The result of the expression should be written to an input/output column, but the data type of the expression cannot be converted to the data type of the column.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4643">0xC004709E</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4643">0xC004709E</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4644">-1073450850</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4644">-1073450850</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4645">DTS_E_EXPREVALCONDITIONALOPINVALIDCONDITIONTYPE</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4645">DTS_E_EXPREVALCONDITIONALOPINVALIDCONDITIONTYPE</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4646">条件运算符的条件表达式“%1”的数据类型“%2”无效。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4646">The conditional expression "%1" of the conditional operator has an invalid data type of "%2".</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4647">此条件运算符的条件表达式必须返回一个类型为 DT_BOOL 的布尔值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4647">The conditional expression of the conditional operator must return a Boolean, which is type DT_BOOL.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4648">0xC004709F</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4648">0xC004709F</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4649">-1073450849</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4649">-1073450849</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4650">DTS_E_EXPREVALCONDITIONALOPTYPEMISMATCH</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4650">DTS_E_EXPREVALCONDITIONALOPTYPEMISMATCH</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4651">数据类型“%1”和“%2”与条件运算符不兼容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4651">The data types "%1" and "%2" are incompatible for the conditional operator.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4652">不能将操作数类型隐式转换为与条件运算兼容的类型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4652">The operand types cannot be implicitly cast into compatible types for the conditional operation.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4653">若要执行此运算，需要使用转换运算符来显式转换两个操作数或其中的一个操作数。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4653">To perform this operation, one or both operands need to be explicitly cast with a cast operator.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4654">0xC00470A0</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4654">0xC00470A0</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4655">-1073450848</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4655">-1073450848</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4656">DTS_E_EXPREVALCONDITIONALOPSETTYPEFAILED</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4656">DTS_E_EXPREVALCONDITIONALOPSETTYPEFAILED</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4657">尝试设置条件运算“%1”的结果类型失败，错误代码为 0x%2!8.8X!。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4657">Attempt to set the result type of conditional operation "%1" failed with error code 0x%2!8.8X!.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4658">0xC00470A1</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4658">0xC00470A1</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4659">-1073450847</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4659">-1073450847</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4660">DTS_E_BUFFERORPHANED</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4660">DTS_E_BUFFERORPHANED</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4661">此缓冲区已被孤立。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4661">This buffer has been orphaned.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4662">缓冲区管理器已关闭，但还有一个未完成的缓冲区，而且不会对该缓冲区执行清除操作。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4662">The buffer manager has shut down, leaving an outstanding buffer and no cleanup will occur for the buffer.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4663">这可能会引起内存泄漏和其他问题。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4663">There is a potential for memory leaks and other problems.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4664">0xC00470A2</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4664">0xC00470A2</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4665">-1073450846</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4665">-1073450846</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4666">DTS_E_EXPREVALINPUTCOLUMNNAMENOTFOUND</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4666">DTS_E_EXPREVALINPUTCOLUMNNAMENOTFOUND</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4667">尝试查找名为“%1”的输入列失败，错误代码为 0x%2!8.8X!。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4667">Attempt to find the input column named "%1" failed with error code 0x%2!8.8X!.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4668">在输入列集合中找不到指定的输入列。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4668">The input column specified was not found in the input column collection.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4669">0xC00470A3</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4669">0xC00470A3</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4670">-1073450845</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4670">-1073450845</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4671">DTS_E_EXPREVALINPUTCOLUMNIDNOTFOUND</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4671">DTS_E_EXPREVALINPUTCOLUMNIDNOTFOUND</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4672">尝试查找沿袭 ID 为 %1!d! 的输入列失败，</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4672">Attempt to find the input column with lineage ID %1!d!</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4673">错误代码为 0x%2!8.8X!。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4673">failed with error code 0x%2!8.8X!.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4674">在输入列集合中找不到此输入列。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4674">The input column was not found in the input column collection.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4675">0xC00470A4</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4675">0xC00470A4</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4676">-1073450844</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4676">-1073450844</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4677">DTS_E_EXPREVALNOINPUTCOLUMNCOLLECTIONFORCOLUMNNAME</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4677">DTS_E_EXPREVALNOINPUTCOLUMNCOLLECTIONFORCOLUMNNAME</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4678">表达式包含无法识别的标记“%1”。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4678">The expression contains unrecognized token "%1".</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4679">如果“%1”是变量，则应将其表示为“\@%1”。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4679">If "%1" is a variable, it should be expressed as "\@%1".</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4680">此指定标记无效。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4680">The specified token is not valid.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4681">如果此标记应用作变量名，它的前缀应为 \@ 符号。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4681">If the token is intended to be a variable name, it should be prefixed with the \@ symbol.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4682">0xC00470A5</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4682">0xC00470A5</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4683">-1073450843</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4683">-1073450843</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4684">DTS_E_EXPREVALNOINPUTCOLUMNCOLLECTIONFORCOLUMNID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4684">DTS_E_EXPREVALNOINPUTCOLUMNCOLLECTIONFORCOLUMNID</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4685">表达式包含无法识别的标记“#%1!d!”。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4685">The expression contains unrecognized token "#%1!d!".</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4686">0xC00470A6</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4686">0xC00470A6</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4687">-1073450842</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4687">-1073450842</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4688">DTS_E_EXPREVALVARIABLENOTFOUND</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4688">DTS_E_EXPREVALVARIABLENOTFOUND</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4689">在 Variables 集合中找不到变量“%1”。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4689">The variable "%1" was not found in the Variables collection.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4690">此变量可能不在正确的作用域内。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4690">The variable might not exist in the correct scope.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4691">0xC00470A7</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4691">0xC00470A7</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4692">-1073450841</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4692">-1073450841</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4693">DTS_E_EXPREVALINVALIDTOKENSTATE</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4693">DTS_E_EXPREVALINVALIDTOKENSTATE</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4694">尝试分析表达式“%1”失败。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4694">Attempt to parse the expression "%1" failed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4695">此表达式可能包含无效标记、不完整标记或无效元素，</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4695">The expression might contain an invalid token, an incomplete token, or an invalid element.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4696">可能格式不正确，也可能缺少某个必需元素的一部分(例如圆括号不成对)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4696">It might not be well-formed, or might be missing part of a required element such as a parenthesis.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4697">0xC00470A8</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4697">0xC00470A8</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4698">-1073450840</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4698">-1073450840</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4699">DTS_E_BLANKOUTPUTCOLUMNNAME</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4699">DTS_E_BLANKOUTPUTCOLUMNNAME</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4700">“%1”的名称为空白，但名称不能为空白。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4700">The name for "%1" is blank, and names cannot be blank.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4701">0xC00470A9</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4701">0xC00470A9</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4702">-1073450839</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4702">-1073450839</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4703">DTS_E_HASSIDEEFFECTSWITHSYNCINP</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4703">DTS_E_HASSIDEEFFECTSWITHSYNCINP</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4704">“%1”的 HasSideEffects 属性设置为 TRUE，但“%1”是同步的，不能有副作用。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4704">The "%1" has the HasSideEffects property set to TRUE, but "%1" is synchronous and cannot have side effects.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4705">请将 HasSideEffects 属性设置为 FALSE。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4705">Set the HasSideEffects property to FALSE.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4706">0xC00470AA</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4706">0xC00470AA</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4707">-1073450838</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4707">-1073450838</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4708">DTS_E_EXPREVALINVALIDCASTCODEPAGE</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4708">DTS_E_EXPREVALINVALIDCASTCODEPAGE</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4709">在向数据类型“%2”转换时，为转换运算的代码页参数指定的值 %1!d! 无效。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4709">The value, %1!d!, specified for the code page parameter of the cast to data type "%2", is not valid.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4710">计算机上没有安装此代码页。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4710">The code page is not installed on the machine.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4711">0xC00470AB</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4711">0xC00470AB</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4712">-1073450837</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4712">-1073450837</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4713">DTS_E_EXPREVALINVALIDCASTPRECISION</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4713">DTS_E_EXPREVALINVALIDCASTPRECISION</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4714">值 %1!d!</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4714">The value %1!d!</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4715">在向数据类型“%2”转换时，为精度参数指定的值 %1!d! 无效。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4715">specified for the precision parameter of the cast to data type "%2" is not valid.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4716">精度必须在 %3!d!</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4716">Precision must be in the range %3!d!</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4717">到 %4!d! 范围内，</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4717">to %4!d!</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4718">但该类型转换运算的精度值超出了此范围。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4718">and the precision value is out of range for the type cast.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4719">0xC00470AC</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4719">0xC00470AC</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4720">-1073450836</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4720">-1073450836</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4721">DTS_E_EXPREVALINVALIDCASTSCALE</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4721">DTS_E_EXPREVALINVALIDCASTSCALE</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4722">值 %1!d!</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4722">The value %1!d!</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4723">在向数据类型“%2”转换时，为小数位数参数指定的值 %1!d! 无效。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4723">specified for the scale parameter of the cast to data type "%2" is not valid.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4724">小数位数必须在 %3!d!</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4724">The scale must be in the range %3!d!</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4725">到 %4!d! 范围内，</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4725">to %4!d!</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4726">但该类型转换运算的小数位数值超出了此范围。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4726">and the scale value is out of range for the type cast.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4727">小数位数不能超过指定的精度且必须为正值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4727">Scale must not exceed precision and must be positive.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4728">0xC00470AD</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4728">0xC00470AD</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4729">-1073450835</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4729">-1073450835</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4730">DTS_E_NONSORTEDOUTPUTHASSORTKEYPOSITIONS</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4730">DTS_E_NONSORTEDOUTPUTHASSORTKEYPOSITIONS</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4731">“%1”的 IsSorted 属性为 False，但其输出列的 SortKeyPositions 的 %2!lu!</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4731">The IsSorted property for "%1" is false, but %2!lu!</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4732">为非零值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4732">of its output columns' SortKeyPositions are non-zero.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4733">0xC00470AF</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4733">0xC00470AF</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4734">-1073450833</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4734">-1073450833</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4735">DTS_E_EXPREVALCONDITIONALOPCODEPAGEMISMATCH</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4735">DTS_E_EXPREVALCONDITIONALOPCODEPAGEMISMATCH</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4736">对于 %2 类型的条件运算“%1”的操作数，它们的代码页必须匹配。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4736">The code pages must match for operands of conditional operation "%1" for type %2.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4737">左操作数的代码页与右操作数的代码页不匹配。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4737">The code page of the left operand does not match the code page of the right operand.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4738">对于指定类型的条件运算符，代码页必须相同。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4738">For the conditional operator on the specified type, the code pages must be the same.</span></span>|

|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4756">0xC00470B4</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4756">0xC00470B4</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4757">-1073450828</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4757">-1073450828</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4758">DTS_E_FILENAMEOUTPUTCOLUMNINVALIDDATATYPE</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4758">DTS_E_FILENAMEOUTPUTCOLUMNINVALIDDATATYPE</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4759">此文件名的输出列不是 Null 结束的 Unicode 字符串，其数据类型为 DT_WSTR。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4759">The output column for the file name is not a null-terminated Unicode character string, which is data type DT_WSTR.</span></span>|

|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4770">0xC00470B7</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4770">0xC00470B7</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4771">-1073450825</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4771">-1073450825</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4772">DTS_E_EXPREVALILLEGALHEXESCAPEINSTRINGLITERAL</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4772">DTS_E_EXPREVALILLEGALHEXESCAPEINSTRINGLITERAL</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4773">字符串文字“%1”包含非法的十六进制转义序列“\x%2”。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4773">The string literal "%1" contains an illegal hexadecimal escape sequence of  "\x%2".</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4774">表达式计算器中的字符串文字不支持此转义序列。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4774">The escape sequence is not supported in string literals in the expression evaluator.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4775">十六进制转义序列的格式必须是 \xhhhh，其中 h 是有效的十六进制数字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4775">The hexadecimal escape sequences must be of the form \xhhhh where h is a valid hexadecimal digit.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4776">0xC00470B8</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4776">0xC00470B8</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4777">-1073450824</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4777">-1073450824</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4778">DTS_E_EXPREVALILLEGALESCAPEINSTRINGLITERAL</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4778">DTS_E_EXPREVALILLEGALESCAPEINSTRINGLITERAL</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4779">字符串文字“%1”包含非法的转义序列“\\%2!c!”。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4779">The string literal "%1" contains an illegal escape sequence of "\\%2!c!".</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4780">表达式计算器中的字符串文字不支持此转义序列。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4780">The escape sequence is not supported in string literals in the expression evaluator.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4781">如果字符串中需要反斜杠，请使用双反斜杠符号 "\\\\"。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4781">If a backslash is needed in the string, use a double backslash, "\\\\".</span></span>|

|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4808">0xC00470BE</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4808">0xC00470BE</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4809">-1073450818</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4809">-1073450818</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4810">DTS_E_EXPREVALUNSUPPORTEDTYPE</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4810">DTS_E_EXPREVALUNSUPPORTEDTYPE</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4811">表达式中不支持数据类型“%1”。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4811">The data type "%1" is not supported in an expression.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4812">不支持指定的类型或该类型无效。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4812">The specified type is not supported or is not valid.</span></span>|

|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4988">0xC00470EC</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4988">0xC00470EC</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4989">-1073450772</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4989">-1073450772</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4990">DTS_E_EXPREVALBINARYOPDTSTRNOTSUPPORTED</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4990">DTS_E_EXPREVALBINARYOPDTSTRNOTSUPPORTED</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4991">对于二元运算的操作数，只有输入列和转换运算才支持数据类型 DT_STR。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4991">For operands of a binary operation, the data type DT_STR is supported only for input columns and cast operations.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4992">表达式“%1”中有一个既非输入列又非转换结果的 DT_STR 操作数，所以不能用于二元运算。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4992">The expression "%1" has a DT_STR operand that is not an input column or the result of a cast, and cannot be used in a binary operation.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-4993">若要执行此运算，需要使用转换运算符显式转换该操作数。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-4993">To perform this operation, the operand needs to be explicitly cast with a cast operator.</span></span>|

|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-5264">0xC0049032</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-5264">0xC0049032</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-5265">-1073442766</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-5265">-1073442766</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-5266">DTS_E_EXPREVALSTATIC_BINARYOPNUMERICOVERFLOW</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-5266">DTS_E_EXPREVALSTATIC_BINARYOPNUMERICOVERFLOW</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-5267">二元运算的结果对于数值类型的最大大小来说太大了。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-5267">The result of a binary operation was too big for the maximum size for numeric types.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-5268">若不降低精度或减少小数位数，就无法将操作数类型隐式转换为数值(DT_NUMERIC)结果。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-5268">The operand types could not be implicitly cast into a numeric (DT_NUMERIC) result without loss of precision or scale.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-5269">若要执行此运算，需要使用转换运算符来显式转换两个操作数或其中的一个操作数。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-5269">To perform this operation, one or both operands need to be explicitly cast with a cast operator.</span></span>|

|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-5451">0xC0049058</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-5451">0xC0049058</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-5452">-1073442728</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-5452">-1073442728</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-5453">DTS_E_EXPREVALSTATIC_INVALIDTOKENSTATE</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-5453">DTS_E_EXPREVALSTATIC_INVALIDTOKENSTATE</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-5454">尝试分析表达式失败。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-5454">Attempt to parse the expression failed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-5455">该表达式包含一个无效或不完整的标记。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-5455">The expression contains an invalid or incomplete token.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-5456">它可能包含无效元素，可能缺少某个必需元素的一部分(如右括号)，也可能格式不正确。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-5456">It may contain invalid elements, be missing part of a required element such as closing parentheses, or may not be well formed.</span></span>|

|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-5591">0xC00490D3</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-5591">0xC00490D3</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-5592">-1073442605</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-5592">-1073442605</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-5593">DTS_E_EXPREVALSTATIC_BINARYOPDTSTRNOTSUPPORTED</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-5593">DTS_E_EXPREVALSTATIC_BINARYOPDTSTRNOTSUPPORTED</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-5594">对于二元运算的操作数，只有输入列和转换运算才支持数据类型 DT_STR。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-5594">For operands of binary operation, the data type DT_STR is only supported for input columns and cast operations.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-5595">如果 DT_STR 操作数不是输入列或转换结果，则不能用于二元运算。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-5595">A DT_STR operand that is not an input column or the result of a cast cannot be used with a binary operation.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-5596">若要执行此运算，需要使用转换运算符显式转换该操作数。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-5596">To perform this operation, the operand needs to be explicitly cast with a cast operator.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-5597">0xC00490D4</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-5597">0xC00490D4</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-5598">-1073442604</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-5598">-1073442604</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-5599">DTS_E_EXPREVALSTATIC_CONDITIONALOPDTSTRNOTSUPPORTED</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-5599">DTS_E_EXPREVALSTATIC_CONDITIONALOPDTSTRNOTSUPPORTED</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-5600">对于条件运算符的操作数，只有输入列和转换运算才支持数据类型 DT_STR。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-5600">For operands of the conditional operator, the data type DT_STR is only supported for input columns and cast operations.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-5601">如果 DT_STR 操作数不是输入列或转换结果，则不能用于条件运算。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-5601">A DT_STR operand that is not an input column or the result of a cast cannot be used with the conditional operation.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-5602">若要执行此运算，需要使用转换运算符显式转换该操作数。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-5602">To perform this operation, the operand needs to be explicitly cast with a cast operator.</span></span>|
