|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-6695">0xC020400F</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-6695">0xC020400F</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-6696">-1071628273</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-6696">-1071628273</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-6697">DTS_E_CANONLYSETSORTKEYONSOURCE</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-6697">DTS_E_CANONLYSETSORTKEYONSOURCE</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-6698">不能将“%1”的 SortKeyPosition 属性设置为非零值，因为“%2”不是源输出。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-6698">The "%1" cannot have a SortKeyPosition property set to non-zero because "%2" is not a source output.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-6699">不能将输出列“colname”(ID)的 SortKeyPosition 属性设置为非零值，因为其输出“outputname”(ID)不是源输出。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-6699">The output column "colname" (ID) cannot have its SortKeyPosition property set to non-zero because its output "outputname" (ID) is not a source output.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-6700">0xC0204010</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-6700">0xC0204010</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-6701">-1071628272</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-6701">-1071628272</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-6702">DTS_E_CANONLYSETCOMPFLAGSONSOURCE</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-6702">DTS_E_CANONLYSETCOMPFLAGSONSOURCE</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-6703">不能将“%1”的 ComparisonFlags 属性设置为非零值，因为“%2”不是源输出。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-6703">The ComparisonFlags property cannot be set to a non-zero value for "%1" because the "%2" is not a source output.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-6704">不能将输出列“colname”(ID)的 ComparisonFlags 属性设置为非零值，因为其输出“outputname”(ID)不是源输出。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-6704">The output column "colname" (ID) cannot have a ComparisonFlags property set to non-zero because its output "outputname" (ID) is not a source output.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-6705">0xC0204011</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-6705">0xC0204011</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-6706">-1071628271</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-6706">-1071628271</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-6707">DTS_E_NONSTRINGCOMPARISONFLAGSNOTZERO</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-6707">DTS_E_NONSTRINGCOMPARISONFLAGSNOTZERO</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-6708">由于“%1”不是字符串类型，所以其比较标志一定为零。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-6708">The comparison flags for "%1" must be zero because its type is not a string type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-6709">只有字符串类型列的 ComparisonFlags 才能为非零。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-6709">ComparisonFlags can only be non-zero for string type columns.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-6710">0xC0204012</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-6710">0xC0204012</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-6711">-1071628270</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-6711">-1071628270</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-6712">DTS_E_COMPFLAGSONLYONSORTCOL</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-6712">DTS_E_COMPFLAGSONLYONSORTCOL</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-6713">不能将“%1”的 ComparisonFlags 属性设置为非零值，因为其 SortKeyPosition 被设置为零。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-6713">The "%1" cannot have a ComparisonFlags property set to non-zero because its SortKeyPosition is set to zero.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-6714">仅当输出列的 SortKeyPosition 也为非零值时，其 ComparisonFlags 才能为非零值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-6714">An output column's ComparisonFlags can only be non-zero if its SortKeyPosition is also non-zero.</span></span>|

|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7109">0xC0208033</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7109">0xC0208033</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7110">-1071611853</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7110">-1071611853</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7111">DTS_E_EXTRACTORCANTAPPENDTRUNCATE</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7111">DTS_E_EXTRACTORCANTAPPENDTRUNCATE</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7112">由于属性设置存在冲突而出错。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7112">Error caused by conflicting property settings.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7113">“%1”的 AllowAppend 属性和 ForceTruncate 属性都被设置为 TRUE。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7113">The "%1" has both the AllowAppend property and the ForceTruncate property set to TRUE.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7114">这两个属性不能同时设置为 TRUE。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7114">Both properties cannot be set to TRUE.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7115">请将其中一个属性设置为 FALSE。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7115">Set one of the two properties to FALSE.</span></span>|

|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7719">0xC02082FF</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7719">0xC02082FF</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7720">-1071611137</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7720">-1071611137</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7721">DTS_E_TXCHARMAP_CANTBOTHCASE</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7721">DTS_E_TXCHARMAP_CANTBOTHCASE</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7722">列“%1”将该列同时映射为大写和小写。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7722">Column "%1" maps the column to both uppercase and lowercase.</span></span>|

|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7731">0xC0208302</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7731">0xC0208302</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7732">-1071611134</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7732">-1071611134</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7733">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_UNSUPPORTED_MATCH_INDEX_VERSION</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7733">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_UNSUPPORTED_MATCH_INDEX_VERSION</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7734">不支持预先存在的匹配索引“%2”的版本(%1)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7734">The version (%1) of the pre-existing match index "%2" is not supported.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7735">预期的版本应为“%3”。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7735">The version expected is "%3".</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7736">如果索引元数据的版本与生成当前代码时针对的版本不匹配，将发生此错误。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7736">This error occurs if the version persisted in the index metadata does not match the version which the current code was built for.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7737">请使用当前版本的代码重新生成索引，以修复此错误。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7737">Fix the error by rebuilding the index with the current version of the code.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7738">0xC0208303</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7738">0xC0208303</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7739">-1071611133</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7739">-1071611133</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7740">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_INVALID_MATCH_INDEX</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7740">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_INVALID_MATCH_INDEX</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7741">表“%1”似乎不是有效的预建匹配索引。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7741">The table "%1" does not appear to be a valid pre-built match index.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7742">当无法从指定的预建索引加载元数据记录时将发生此错误。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7742">This error occurs if the metadata record cannot be loaded from the specified pre-built index.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7743">0xC0208304</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7743">0xC0208304</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7744">-1071611132</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7744">-1071611132</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7745">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_UNABLE_TO_READ_MATCH_INDEX</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7745">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_UNABLE_TO_READ_MATCH_INDEX</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7746">无法读取指定的预建匹配索引“%1”。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7746">Unable to read specified pre-built match index "%1".</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7747">OLEDB 错误代码:0x%2!8.8X!。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7747">OLEDB Error code: 0x%2!8.8X!.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7748">0xC0208305</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7748">0xC0208305</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7749">-1071611131</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7749">-1071611131</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7750">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_NO_JOIN_COLUMNS</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7750">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_NO_JOIN_COLUMNS</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7751">没有任何输入列具有到引用表列的有效联接。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7751">There were no input columns with a valid join to a reference table column.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7752">请确保至少有一个联接是使用输入列属性 JoinToReferenceColumn 和 JoinType 定义的。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7752">Make sure that there is at least one join defined using the input column properties JoinToReferenceColumn and JoinType.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7753">0xC0208306</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7753">0xC0208306</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7754">-1071611130</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7754">-1071611130</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7755">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_INDEX_DOES_NOT_CONTAIN_COLUMN</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7755">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_INDEX_DOES_NOT_CONTAIN_COLUMN</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7756">指定的预先存在的匹配索引“%1”不是使用模糊匹配信息为列“%2”生成的。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7756">The specified pre-existing match index "%1" was not originally built with fuzzy match information for column "%2".</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7757">必须重新生成此索引以包含该信息。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7757">It must be rebuilt to include this information.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7758">当生成索引所使用的列不是模糊联接列时，将发生此错误。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7758">This error occurs when the index was built with the column not being a fuzzy join column.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7759">0xC0208307</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7759">0xC0208307</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7760">-1071611129</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7760">-1071611129</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7761">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_IDENTIFIER_PROPERTY</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7761">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_IDENTIFIER_PROPERTY</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7762">为属性“%2”提供的名称“%1”不是有效的 SQL 标识符名称。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7762">The name "%1" given for property "%2" is not a valid SQL identifier name.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7763">如果属性名称不符合有效 SQL 标识符名称的规范，将发生此错误。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7763">This error occurs if the name for the property does not conform to the specifications for a valid SQL identifier name.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7764">0xC0208309</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7764">0xC0208309</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7765">-1071611127</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7765">-1071611127</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7766">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_MINSIMILARITY_INVALID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7766">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_MINSIMILARITY_INVALID</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7767">为模糊查找转换设置的 MinSimilarity 阈值属性的值必须大于等于 0.0 且小于 1.0。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7767">The MinSimilarity threshold property on the Fuzzy Lookup transformation must be a value greater than or equal to 0.0 but less than 1.0.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7768">0xC020830A</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7768">0xC020830A</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7769">-1071611126</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7769">-1071611126</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7770">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_INVALID_PROPERTY_VALUE</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7770">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_INVALID_PROPERTY_VALUE</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7771">属性“%2”的值“%1”无效。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7771">The value "%1" for property "%2" is not valid.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7772">0xC020830B</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7772">0xC020830B</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7773">-1071611125</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7773">-1071611125</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7774">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_INCOMPATIBLE_FUZZY_JOIN_DATATYPES</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7774">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_INCOMPATIBLE_FUZZY_JOIN_DATATYPES</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7775">输入列“%1”与引用列“%2”之间的指定模糊查找无效，因为仅支持类型为 DT_STR 和 DT_WSTR 的字符串列之间的模糊联接。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7775">The fuzzy lookup specified between input column "%1" and reference column "%2" is not valid because fuzzy joins are only supported between string columns, types DT_STR and DT_WSTR.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7776">0xC020830C</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7776">0xC020830C</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7777">-1071611124</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7777">-1071611124</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7778">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_INCOMPATIBLE_EXACT_JOIN_DATATYPES</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7778">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_INCOMPATIBLE_EXACT_JOIN_DATATYPES</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7779">完全查找列“%1”和“%2”的数据类型不相同或不是类似的字符串类型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7779">The exact lookup columns, "%1" and "%2", do not have equal data types or are not comparable string types.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7780">支持以下类型列之间的完全联接: 数据类型相同或是 DT_STR 与 DT_WSTR 组合。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7780">Exact joins are supported between columns with equal data types or a DT_STR and DT_WSTR combination.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7781">0xC020830D</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7781">0xC020830D</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7782">-1071611123</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7782">-1071611123</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7783">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_INCOMPATIBLE_COPYCOLUMN_DATATYPES</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7783">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_INCOMPATIBLE_COPYCOLUMN_DATATYPES</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7784">复制列“%1”与“%2”的数据类型不相同或者是完全无法转换的字符串类型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7784">The copy columns, "%1" and "%2", do not have equal data types or are not trivially convertible string types.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7785">发生这种情况，是由于支持以下类型列之间从引用到输出的复制: 数据类型相同或是 DT_STR 与 DT_WSTR 组合，但不支持其他类型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7785">This occurs because copying from reference to output between columns with equal data types, or a DT_STR and DT_WSTR combination, is supported, but other types are not.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7786">0xC020830E</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7786">0xC020830E</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7787">-1071611122</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7787">-1071611122</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7788">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_INCOMPATIBLE_PASSTHRUCOLUMN_DATATYPES</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7788">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_INCOMPATIBLE_PASSTHRUCOLUMN_DATATYPES</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7789">传递列“%1”与“%2”的数据类型不相同。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7789">The passthrough columns, "%1" and "%2", do not have equal data types.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7790">只有具有相同数据类型的列才能作为从输入到输出的传递列。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7790">Only columns with equal data types are supported as passthrough columns from input to output.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7791">0xC020830F</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7791">0xC020830F</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7792">-1071611121</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7792">-1071611121</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7793">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_UNABLETOLOCATEREFCOLUMN</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7793">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_UNABLETOLOCATEREFCOLUMN</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7794">找不到引用列“%1”。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7794">Cannot locate reference column "%1".</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7795">0xC0208311</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7795">0xC0208311</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7796">-1071611119</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7796">-1071611119</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7797">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_OUTPUT_COLUMN_MUST_BE_PASSTHRU_COLUMN_OR_A_COPY_COLUMN</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7797">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_OUTPUT_COLUMN_MUST_BE_PASSTHRU_COLUMN_OR_A_COPY_COLUMN</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7798">必须为输出列指定一个且只能指定一个 CopyColumn 或 PassThruColumn 属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7798">An output column must have exactly one CopyColumn or PassThruColumn property specified.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7799">当 CopyColumn 属性和 PassThruColumn 属性都被设置为非空值，或当 CopyColumn 属性和 PassThruColumn 属性都未被设置为非空值时，会发生此错误。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7799">This error occurs when neither the CopyColumn or the PassThruColumn properties, or both the CopyColumn and PassThruColumn properties, are set to non-empty values.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7800">0xC0208312</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7800">0xC0208312</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7801">-1071611118</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7801">-1071611118</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7802">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_PASSTHRU_COLUMN_NOT_FOUND</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7802">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_PASSTHRU_COLUMN_NOT_FOUND</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7803">在输入列集合中找不到为输出列“%3”的属性“%2”指定的源沿袭 ID“%1!d!”</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7803">The source lineage id '%1!d!'</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7804">。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7804">specified for property '%2' on output column '%3' was not found in the input column collection.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7805">如果在输入集内找不到在输出列上被指定为传递列的输入列 ID 时，将发生此错误。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7805">This occurs when the input column id specified on an output column as a passthrough column is not found in the set of inputs.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7806">0xC0208313</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7806">0xC0208313</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7807">-1071611117</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7807">-1071611117</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7808">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_INDEXED_COLUMN_NOT_FOUND_IN_REF_TABLE</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7808">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_INDEXED_COLUMN_NOT_FOUND_IN_REF_TABLE</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7809">在引用表/查询中找不到预建索引“%2”中的列“%1”。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7809">The column "%1" in the pre-built index "%2" was not found in the reference table/query.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7810">如果在生成预先存在的匹配索引之后，引用表的架构/查询发生了更改，将出现这种情况。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7810">This happens if the schema/query of the reference table has changed since the pre-existing match index was built.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7811">0xC0208314</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7811">0xC0208314</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7812">-1071611116</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7812">-1071611116</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7813">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_TOKEN_TOO_LONG</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7813">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_TOKEN_TOO_LONG</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7814">组件遇到超过 2147483647 个字符的标记。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7814">The component encountered a token that was larger than 2147483647 characters.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7815">0xC0208315</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7815">0xC0208315</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7816">-1071611115</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7816">-1071611115</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7817">DTS_E_RAWMETADATAMISMATCHTYPE</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7817">DTS_E_RAWMETADATAMISMATCHTYPE</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7818">无法追加输出文件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7818">The output file cannot be appended.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7819">列“%1”是按名称匹配的，而文件中列的类型为 %2，输入列的类型为 %3。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7819">Column "%1" matches by name, but the column in the file has type %2 and the input column has type %3.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7820">列的元数据的数据类型不匹配。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7820">The metadata for the column does not match on data type.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7821">0xC0208316</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7821">0xC0208316</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7822">-1071611114</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7822">-1071611114</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7823">DTS_E_RAWMETADATAMISMATCHSIZE</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7823">DTS_E_RAWMETADATAMISMATCHSIZE</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7824">无法追加输出文件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7824">The output file cannot be appended.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7825">列“%1”是按名称匹配的，而该文件中相应列的最大长度为 %2!d!，</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7825">Column "%1" matches by name, but the column in the file has maximum length %2!d!</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7826">输入列的最大长度为 %3!d!。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7826">and the input column has maximum length %3!d!.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7827">列的元数据的长度不匹配。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7827">The metadata for the column does not match in length.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7828">0xC0208317</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7828">0xC0208317</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7829">-1071611113</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7829">-1071611113</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7830">DTS_E_RAWMETADATAMISMATCHCODEPAGE</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7830">DTS_E_RAWMETADATAMISMATCHCODEPAGE</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7831">无法追加输出文件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7831">The output file cannot be appended.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7832">列“%1”是按名称匹配的，而文件列的代码页为 %2!d!，</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7832">Column "%1" matches by name, but the column in the file has code page %2!d!</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7833">输入列的代码页为 %3!d!。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7833">and the input column has code page %3!d!.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7834">指定列的元数据的代码页不匹配。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7834">The metadata for the named column does not match on code page.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7835">0xC0208318</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7835">0xC0208318</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7836">-1071611112</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7836">-1071611112</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7837">DTS_E_RAWMETADATAMISMATCHPRECISION</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7837">DTS_E_RAWMETADATAMISMATCHPRECISION</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7838">无法追加输出文件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7838">The output file cannot be appended.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7839">列“%1”是按名称匹配的，而文件列的精度为 %2!d!，</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7839">Column "%1" matches by name, but the column in the file has precision %2!d!</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7840">输入列的精度为 %3!d!。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7840">and the input column has precision %3!d!.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7841">指定列的元数据的精度不匹配。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7841">The metadata for the named column does not match on precision.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7842">0xC0208319</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7842">0xC0208319</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7843">-1071611111</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7843">-1071611111</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7844">DTS_E_RAWMETADATAMISMATCHSCALE</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7844">DTS_E_RAWMETADATAMISMATCHSCALE</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7845">无法追加输出文件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7845">The output file cannot be appended.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7846">列“%1”是按名称匹配的，而文件列的小数位数为 %2!d!，</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7846">Column "%1" matches by name, but the column in the file has scale %2!d!</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7847">输入列的小数位数为 %3!d!。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7847">and the input column has scale %3!d!.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7848">指定列的元数据的小数位数不匹配。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7848">The metadata for the named column does not match on scale.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7849">0xC020831A</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7849">0xC020831A</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7850">-1071611110</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7850">-1071611110</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7851">DTS_E_COULD_NOT_DETERMINE_DATASOURCE_DBMSNAME</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7851">DTS_E_COULD_NOT_DETERMINE_DATASOURCE_DBMSNAME</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7852">无法确定“%1”的 DBMS 名称和版本。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7852">Unable to determine the DBMS name and version on "%1".</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7853">如果连接的 IDBProperties 未返回验证 DBMS 名称和版本所需的信息，将出现这种情况。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7853">This occurs if the IDBProperties on the connection did not return information needed to verify the DBMS name and version.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7854">0xC020831B</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7854">0xC020831B</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7855">-1071611109</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7855">-1071611109</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7856">DTS_E_INCORRECT_SQL_SERVER_VERSION</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7856">DTS_E_INCORRECT_SQL_SERVER_VERSION</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7857">不支持的“%1”DBMS 类型或版本。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7857">The DBMS type or version of "%1" is not supported.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7858">必须建立与 Microsoft SQL Server 8.0 版或更高版本的连接。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7858">A connection to Microsoft SQL Server version 8.0 or later is required.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7859">如果连接的 IDBProperties 未返回正确的版本信息，将出现这种情况。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7859">This occurs if IDBProperties on the connection did not return a the correct version.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7860">0xC020831D</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7860">0xC020831D</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7861">-1071611107</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7861">-1071611107</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7862">DTS_E_CANTDELETEERRORCOLUMNS</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7862">DTS_E_CANTDELETEERRORCOLUMNS</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7863">%1 是一种特殊的错误输出列，无法删除。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7863">The %1 is a special error output column and cannot be deleted.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7864">0xC020831E</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7864">0xC020831E</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7865">-1071611106</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7865">-1071611106</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7866">DTS_E_UNEXPECTEDCOLUMNDATATYPE</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7866">DTS_E_UNEXPECTEDCOLUMNDATATYPE</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7867">为列“%1”指定的数据类型不是所需的类型“%2”。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7867">The data type specified for column "%1" is not the expected type "%2".</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7868">0xC020831F</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7868">0xC020831F</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7869">-1071611105</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7869">-1071611105</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7870">DTS_E_INPUTCOLUMNNOTFOUND</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7870">DTS_E_INPUTCOLUMNNOTFOUND</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7871">在输入列集合中找不到由输出列“%3”的属性“%2”引用的输入列沿袭 ID“%1”。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7871">The input column lineage ID "%1" referenced by property "%2" on output column "%3" could not be located in the input column collection.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7872">0xC0208320</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7872">0xC0208320</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7873">-1071611104</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7873">-1071611104</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7874">DTS_E_TXGROUPDUPS_INPUTCOLUMNNOTJOINED</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7874">DTS_E_TXGROUPDUPS_INPUTCOLUMNNOTJOINED</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7875">由输出列“%3”的“%2”属性引用的输入列“%1”，必须将 ToBeCleaned 属性设置为 True，还必须有一个有效的 ExactFuzzy 属性值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7875">The input column "%1" referenced by the "%2" property on output column "%3" must have property ToBeCleaned=True and have a valid ExactFuzzy property value.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7876">0xC0208322</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7876">0xC0208322</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7877">-1071611102</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7877">-1071611102</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7878">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_REF_TABLE_MISSING_IDENTITY_INDEX</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7878">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_REF_TABLE_MISSING_IDENTITY_INDEX</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7879">引用表“%1”没有整数标识列的聚集索引，如果将属性“CopyRefTable”设置为 FALSE，此索引是必需的。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7879">The reference table '%1' does not have a clustered index on an integer identity column, which is required if the property 'CopyRefTable' is set to FALSE.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7880">如果 CopyRefTable 为 False，引用表必须具有整数标识列的聚集索引。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7880">If CopyRefTable is false, the reference table must have a clustered index on an integer identity column.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7881">0xC0208323</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7881">0xC0208323</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7882">-1071611101</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7882">-1071611101</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7883">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_REF_CONTAINS_NON_INTEGER_IDENT_COLUMN</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7883">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_REF_CONTAINS_NON_INTEGER_IDENT_COLUMN</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7884">引用表“%1”包含不支持的非整数类型标识列。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7884">The reference table '%1' contains a non-integer type identity column which is not supported.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7885">请使用不包含列“%2”的表视图。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7885">Use a view of the table without the column '%2'.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7886">出现这种错误的原因是，复制引用表时，添加了一个整数标识列，而每个表只允许有一个整数标识列。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7886">This error occurs  because when a copy is made of the reference table, an integer identity column is added, and only one identity column is allowed per table.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7887">0xC0208324</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7887">0xC0208324</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7888">-1071611100</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7888">-1071611100</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7889">DTS_E_TXFUZZY_MATCHCONTRIBUTION_AND_HIERARCHY_SPECIFIED</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7889">DTS_E_TXFUZZY_MATCHCONTRIBUTION_AND_HIERARCHY_SPECIFIED</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7890">不能同时指定 MatchContribution 和层次结构信息。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7890">Both MatchContribution and hierarchy information cannot be specified at the same time.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7891">由于这两个属性都是记分所使用的加权系数，因此不允许这样做。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7891">This is not allowed because these properties are both weighing factors for scoring.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7892">0xC0208325</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7892">0xC0208325</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7893">-1071611099</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7893">-1071611099</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7894">DTS_E_TXFUZZY_HIERARCHY_INCORRECT</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7894">DTS_E_TXFUZZY_HIERARCHY_INCORRECT</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7895">层次结构中表示级别的数字必须唯一。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7895">Levels in hierarchy should be unique numbers .</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7896">层次结构中的有效级别值是大于或等于 1 的整数。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7896">Valid  level in hierarchy values are integers greater than or equal to 1.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7897">数字越小，列在层次结构中的级别越低。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7897">The smaller the number is, the lower the column is in the hierarchy.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7898">默认值为 0，表示列不属于层次结构。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7898">The default value is 0, indicating that the column is not part of a hierarchy.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7899">不允许出现重叠和间断。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7899">Overlaps and gaps are not allowed.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7900">0xC0208326</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7900">0xC0208326</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7901">-1071611098</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7901">-1071611098</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7902">DTS_E_TXFUZZYGROUPING_INSUFFICIENT_FUZZY_JOIN_COLUMNS</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7902">DTS_E_TXFUZZYGROUPING_INSUFFICIENT_FUZZY_JOIN_COLUMNS</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7903">没有定义要作为模糊分组依据的列。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7903">No columns to fuzzy group on were defined.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7904">至少必须有一个输入列的属性是 ToBeCleaned=true 和 ExactFuzzy=2。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7904">There must be at least one input column with column properties ToBeCleaned=true and ExactFuzzy=2.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7905">0xC0208329</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7905">0xC0208329</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7906">-1071611095</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7906">-1071611095</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7907">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_COLUMNINVALID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7907">DTS_E_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_COLUMNINVALID</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7908">未知原因导致 ID 为“%1!d!”</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7908">The column with ID '%1!d!'</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-7909">的列无效。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-7909">was not valid for an undetermined reason.</span></span>|

|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9672">0x80047007</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9672">0x80047007</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9673">-2147192825</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9673">-2147192825</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9674">DTS_W_NOLINEAGEVALIDATION</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9674">DTS_W_NOLINEAGEVALIDATION</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9675">由于执行树包含循环，无法验证输入列的沿袭 ID。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9675">The lineage IDs of the input columns cannot be validated because the execution trees contain cycles.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9676">0x80047034</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9676">0x80047034</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9677">-2147192780</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9677">-2147192780</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9678">DTS_W_EMPTYDATAFLOW</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9678">DTS_W_EMPTYDATAFLOW</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9679">DataFlow 任务中没有组件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9679">The DataFlow task has no components.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9680">请向任务添加组件，或者删除任务。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9680">Add components or remove the task.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9681">0x80047069</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9681">0x80047069</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9682">-2147192727</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9682">-2147192727</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9683">DTS_W_SORTEDOUTPUTHASNOSORTKEYPOSITIONS</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9683">DTS_W_SORTEDOUTPUTHASNOSORTKEYPOSITIONS</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9684">%1 的 IsSorted 属性设置为 TRUE，但其所有输出列的 SortKeyPositions 都被设置为零。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9684">The IsSorted property of %1 is set to TRUE, but all of its output columns' SortKeyPositions are set to zero.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9685">0x8004706F</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9685">0x8004706F</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9686">-2147192721</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9686">-2147192721</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9687">DTS_W_SOURCEREMOVED</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9687">DTS_W_SOURCEREMOVED</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9688">将不读取源“%1”(%2!d!)，因为它的所有数据在数据流任务外均不可见。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9688">Source "%1" (%2!d!) will not be read because none of its data ever becomes visible outside the Data Flow Task.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9689">0x80047076</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9689">0x80047076</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9690">-2147192714</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9690">-2147192714</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9691">DTS_W_UNUSEDOUTPUTDATA</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9691">DTS_W_UNUSEDOUTPUTDATA</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9692">输出“%3”(%4!d!)和组件“%5”(%6!d!)的输出列“%1”(%2!d!)以后不在数据流任务中使用。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9692">The output column "%1" (%2!d!) on output "%3" (%4!d!) and component "%5" (%6!d!) is not subsequently used in the Data Flow task.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9693">删除此不用的输出列可以提高数据流任务的性能。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9693">Removing this unused output column can increase Data Flow task performance.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9694">0x800470AE</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9694">0x800470AE</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9695">-2147192658</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9695">-2147192658</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9696">DTS_W_COMPONENTREMOVED</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9696">DTS_W_COMPONENTREMOVED</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9697">组件的“%1”(%2!d!)输出未使用，且其输入无其他作用，或者其未连接到其他组件的输出，因此已将其从数据流任务中删除。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9697">Component "%1" (%2!d!) has been removed from the Data Flow task because its output is not used and its inputs either have no side effects or are not connected to outputs of other components.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9698">如果需要该组件，应至少将它的一个输入的 HasSideEffects 属性设置为 True，或者将它的输出连接到某个对象。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9698">If the component is required, then the HasSideEffects property on at least one of its inputs should be set to true, or its output should be connected to something.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9699">0x800470B0</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9699">0x800470B0</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9700">-2147192656</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9700">-2147192656</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9701">DTS_W_NOWORKTODO</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9701">DTS_W_NOWORKTODO</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9702">为某个线程指定了行，但该线程没有要完成的工作。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9702">Rows were given to a thread, but that thread has no work to do.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9703">布局有连接已断开的输出。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9703">The layout has a disconnected output.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9704">将 RunInOptimizedMode 属性设置为 TRUE，管道将运行得更快，并可避免出现此警告。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9704">Running the pipeline with the RunInOptimizedMode property set to TRUE will be faster, and prevents this warning.</span></span>|

|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9792">0x8020820C</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9792">0x8020820C</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9793">-2145353204</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9793">-2145353204</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9794">DTS_W_UNMAPPEDINPUTCOLUMN</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9794">DTS_W_UNMAPPEDINPUTCOLUMN</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9795">位于索引 %3!d! 处 ID 为 %2!d!</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9795">The input column "%1" with ID %2!d!</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9796">的输入列“%1”</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9796">at index %3!d!</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9797">已被取消映射。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9797">is unmapped.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9798">该列的沿袭 ID 为零。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9798">The lineage ID for the column is zero.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9799">0x80208305</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9799">0x80208305</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9800">-2145352955</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9800">-2145352955</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9801">DTS_W_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_DELIMITERS_DONT_MATCH</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9801">DTS_W_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_DELIMITERS_DONT_MATCH</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9802">指定的分隔符与用于生成预先存在的匹配索引“%1”的分隔符不匹配。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9802">The specified delimiters do not match the delimiters used to build the pre-existing match index "%1".</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9803">当用于标记字段的分隔符相互不匹配时，就会出现此错误。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9803">This error occurs when the delimiters used to tokenize fields do not match.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9804">这将对匹配行为或结果产生未知的影响。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9804">This can have unknown effects on the matching behavior or results.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9805">0x80208308</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9805">0x80208308</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9806">-2145352952</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9806">-2145352952</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9807">DTS_W_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_MAXRESULTS_IS_ZERO</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9807">DTS_W_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_MAXRESULTS_IS_ZERO</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9808">模糊查找转换的 MaxOutputMatchesPerInput 属性为零。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9808">The MaxOutputMatchesPerInput property on the Fuzzy Lookup transformation is zero.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9809">将不生成任何结果。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9809">No results will be produced.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9810">0x80208310</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9810">0x80208310</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9811">-2145352944</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9811">-2145352944</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9812">DTS_W_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_NO_FUZZY_JOIN_COLUMNS</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9812">DTS_W_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_NO_FUZZY_JOIN_COLUMNS</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9813">没有 JoinType 列属性设置为 Fuzzy 的有效输入列。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9813">There were no valid input columns with JoinType column property set to Fuzzy.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9814">使用查找转换而不是模糊查找可以改进完全联接的性能。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9814">Performance on Exact joins may be improved by using the Lookup transform instead of FuzzyLookup.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9815">0x8020831C</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9815">0x8020831C</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9816">-2145352932</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9816">-2145352932</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9817">DTS_W_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_TIMESTAMPCAVEAT</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9817">DTS_W_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_TIMESTAMPCAVEAT</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9818">引用列“%1”可以是 SQL 时间戳列。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9818">The reference column "%1" may be a SQL timestamp column.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9819">如果生成模糊匹配索引，并且生成引用表的副本，则所有引用表时间戳都将反映生成副本时该表的当前状态。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9819">When the fuzzy match index is built, and a copy of the reference table is made, all reference table timestamps will reflect the current state of the table at the time of the copy.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9820">如果 CopyReferenceTable 设置为 False，则可能发生意外行为。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9820">Unexpected behavior may occur if the CopyReferenceTable is set to false.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9821">0x80208321</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9821">0x80208321</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9822">-2145352927</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9822">-2145352927</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9823">DTS_W_MATCHINDEXALREADYEXISTS</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9823">DTS_W_MATCHINDEXALREADYEXISTS</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9824">为 MatchIndexName 提供的名为“%1”的表已经存在，并且 DropExistingMatchIndex 设置为 FALSE。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9824">A table with the name '%1' given for MatchIndexName already exists and DropExistingMatchIndex is set to FALSE.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9825">除非删除此表，或指定其他名称，或将 DropExisitingMatchIndex 设置为 TRUE，否则转换将失败。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9825">Transform execution will fail unless this table is dropped, a different name is specified, or DropExisitingMatchIndex is set to TRUE.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9826">0x8020832B</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9826">0x8020832B</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9827">-2145352917</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9827">-2145352917</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9828">DTS_W_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_JOINLENGTHMISMATCH</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9828">DTS_W_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_JOINLENGTHMISMATCH</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9829">输入列“%1”的长度与它要匹配的引用列“%2”的长度不相等。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9829">The length of input column '%1' is not equal to the length of the reference column '%2' that it is being matched against.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9830">0x8020832D</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9830">0x8020832D</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9831">-2145352915</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9831">-2145352915</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9832">DTS_W_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_CODEPAGE_MISMATCH</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9832">DTS_W_TXFUZZYLOOKUP_CODEPAGE_MISMATCH</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9833">DT_STR 源列“%1”的代码页和 DT_STR 目标列“%2”的代码页不匹配。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9833">The code pages of the DT_STR source column "%1" and the DT_STR dest column "%2" do not match.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9834">这可能导致意外结果。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9834">This may cause unexpected results.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9835">0x8020832E</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9835">0x8020832E</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9836">-2145352914</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9836">-2145352914</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9837">DTS_W_FUZZYLOOKUP_TOOMANYEXACTMATCHCOLUMNS</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9837">DTS_W_FUZZYLOOKUP_TOOMANYEXACTMATCHCOLUMNS</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9838">完全匹配联接多于 16 个，因此性能可能并非最佳。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9838">There are more than 16 exact match joins, so performance may not be optimal.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9839">请减少完全匹配联接的数目以改进性能。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9839">Reduce the number of exact match joins to improve performance.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9840">SQL Server 将每个索引的列数限制为 16 个，倒排索引将用于全部查找。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9840">SQL Server has a limit of 16 columns per index, the inverted index will be used for all lookups.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9841">0x80208350</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9841">0x80208350</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9842">-2145352880</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9842">-2145352880</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9843">DTS_W_FUZZYLOOKUP_MEMLIMITANDEXHAUSTIVESPECIFIED</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9843">DTS_W_FUZZYLOOKUP_MEMLIMITANDEXHAUSTIVESPECIFIED</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9844">Exhaustive 选项要求将整个引用表加载到主内存中。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9844">The Exhaustive option requires that the entire reference be loaded into main memory.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9845">但是，由于已为 MaxMemoryUsage 属性指定了内存上限值，所以可能无法加载整个引用表，从而导致匹配操作在运行时失败。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9845">Since a memory limit has been specified for the MaxMemoryUsage property, it is possible that the entire reference table will not fit within this bound and that the match operation will fail at runtime.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9846">0x80208351</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9846">0x80208351</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9847">-2145352879</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9847">-2145352879</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9848">DTS_W_FUZZYLOOKUP_EXACTMATCHCOLUMNSEXCEEDBYTELIMIT</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9848">DTS_W_FUZZYLOOKUP_EXACTMATCHCOLUMNSEXCEEDBYTELIMIT</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9849">完全匹配联接中指定的列的累计长度超过了索引键 900 个字节的长度限制。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9849">The cumulative lengths of the columns specified in the exact match joins exceeds the 900 byte limit for index keys.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9850">模糊查找为完全匹配列创建索引以提高查找性能，但此索引有可能无法创建，此时查找仍将使用可能速度较慢的替代方法查找匹配项。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9850">Fuzzy Lookup creates an index on the exact match columns to increase lookup performance and there is a possibility that creation of this index may fail and the lookup will fall back to an alternative, possibly slower, method of finding matches.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9851">如果性能有问题，请尝试删除一些完全匹配联接列，或减小可变长度完全匹配列的最大长度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9851">If performance is a problem, try removing some exact match join columns or reduce the maximum lengths of variable length exact match columns.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9852">0x80208352</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9852">0x80208352</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9853">-2145352878</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9853">-2145352878</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9854">DTS_W_FUZZYLOOKUP_EXACTMATCHINDEXCREATIONFAILED</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9854">DTS_W_FUZZYLOOKUP_EXACTMATCHINDEXCREATIONFAILED</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9855">无法为完全匹配列创建索引。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9855">Failed to create an index for exact match columns.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9856">仍然使用替代的模糊查找方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9856">Reverting to alternative fuzzy lookup method.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9857">0x80208353</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9857">0x80208353</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9858">-2145352877</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9858">-2145352877</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9859">DTS_W_FUZZYGROUPINGINTERNALPIPELINEWARNING</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9859">DTS_W_FUZZYGROUPINGINTERNALPIPELINEWARNING</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9860">出现警告代码为 0x%1!8.8X! 的以下模糊分组内部管道警告:“%2”。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9860">The following Fuzzy Grouping internal pipeline warning occurred with warning code 0x%1!8.8X!: "%2".</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9861">0x80208375</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9861">0x80208375</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9862">-2145352843</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9862">-2145352843</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9863">DTS_W_XMLSRCOUTPUTCOLUMNLENGTHSETTODEFAULT</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9863">DTS_W_XMLSRCOUTPUTCOLUMNLENGTHSETTODEFAULT</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9864">没有为外部数据类型为 %2 的 %1 指定最大长度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9864">No maximum length was specified for the %1 with external data type %2.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9865">将使用长度为 %4!d! 的 SSIS 数据流任务数据类型“%3”</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9865">The SSIS Data Flow Task data type "%3" with a length of %4!d!</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9866">。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9866">will be used.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9867">0x80208376</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9867">0x80208376</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9868">-2145352842</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9868">-2145352842</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9869">DTS_W_XMLSRCOUTPUTCOLUMNDATATYPEMAPPEDTOSTRING</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9869">DTS_W_XMLSRCOUTPUTCOLUMNDATATYPEMAPPEDTOSTRING</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9870">%1 引用了无法映射为 SSIS 数据流任务数据类型的外部数据类型 %2。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9870">The %1 references external data type %2, which cannot be mapped to a SSIS Data Flow Task data type.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9871">将改用长度为 %3!d! 的 SSIS 数据流任务数据类型 DT_WSTR</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9871">The SSIS Data Flow Task data type DT_WSTR with a length of %3!d!</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9872">。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9872">will be used instead.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9873">0x80208385</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9873">0x80208385</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9874">-2145352827</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9874">-2145352827</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9875">DTS_W_NOREDIRECTWITHATTACHEDERROROUTPUTS</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9875">DTS_W_NOREDIRECTWITHATTACHEDERROROUTPUTS</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9876">将不会向错误输出发送任何行。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9876">No rows will be sent to error output(s).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9877">请对错误处理或截断处理进行配置，使行重定向到错误输出，或删除附加到错误输出后的数据流转换或数据流目标。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9877">Configure error or truncation dispositions to redirect rows to the error output(s), or delete data flow transformations or destinations that are attached to the error output(s).</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9878">0x80208386</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9878">0x80208386</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9879">-2145352826</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9879">-2145352826</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9880">DTS_W_REDIRECTWITHNOATTACHEDERROROUTPUTS</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9880">DTS_W_REDIRECTWITHNOATTACHEDERROROUTPUTS</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9881">发送到错误输出的行将丢失。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9881">Rows sent to the error output(s) will be lost.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d51e-9882">请添加新的数据流转换或数据流目标来接收错误输出，或对组件进行重新配置，停止将行重定向到错误输出。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d51e-9882">Add new data flow transformations or destinations to receive error rows, or reconfigure the component to stop redirecting rows to the error output(s).</span></span>|
